final_desc: - - Dalam kemasan 2 l atau kurang :Minuman fermentasi (wine) dari buah anggur segar, termasuk minuman fermentasi (wine) yang diperkuat; grape must selain dari pos 20.09.;- - In containers holding 2 l or less :Wine of fresh grapes, including fortified wines; grape must other than that of heading 20.09.
